title: Guts and Glory v0.8.0
description: Welcome to Guts and Glory -- The craziest game show on earth, where ordinary people compete in extraordinary challenges of life and death, for glory!The objective is simple:  Race to the finish line while everything tries to kill you.Dodge spinning saw blades, deadly spikes, explosives, turrets, and a growing list of other hazardshile navigating insane tracks set in a wide variety of environments.  A game full of LOLs and WTFs and OMGs, where failing can be just as much fun as winning.  Do it
